&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a Ward Clerk to join the team on Eden Ward You must be able to demonstrate good communication skills and work closely with all members of the multi-disciplinary team, meet the person specification and be able to perform under pressure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will have experience in a health care environment and must have good verbal and written communication skills, be a caring person who is well organised, able to respond to changing priorities and have the ability to work under pressure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This a full time post: 37.5 hours per week.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lisa Jeffery, Ward Sister. Email address: lisa.jeffery2@nhs.net Tel: 01872 252090&lt;/p&gt;
